  "comment": "Ovation P-56WW is a bright, compact, and virtually silent par with exceptionally high CRI that is ideal for theatrical and studio applications. The sleek, modern-style par produces a homogenized, single-source, flat and even field of light with the same efficient warm white LED system found in the award-winning Ovation E-260WW ellipsoidal. Interchangeable lens plates are included for narrow, medium and wide beam angles. The virtually silent par also features extremely smooth 16-bit dimming, as well as RDM and PWM for set-up ease. The unit accepts standard 7.5” beam shaping accessories.",
